}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This hub uses the old greyish color scheme.
"HU2140G2 VER:1.3" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :This hub is using all '''S.I.''' capacitors.
The power adapter included with the device is a '''Jentec''' AF1805-A (100-120VAC ~ 50-60Hz, 0.4A -> 5VDC 2.5A).
The copyright year on the box is 2003. The copyright year on the included QIG is 2004.
